`(It) burned their father and when he burned he went into the river but it didn't help.'

\ea%x938
\label{ex:x938}
\gll Ufer-iwkin  urup-em-ik-eya  [yos=ke]\textsubscript{S}  mik-a-m. \\
      \\
\glt
\z

